  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever strolled through your local mall and thought to yourself: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“I could totally build something like this myself!”</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Well, now you can!</strong> Mall Craze is a Shopping Center Management game where you become the architect and owner of your very own mall! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/8821429ef5fbd3d97503b707f14d2f3d.poster.avif?t=1737972661\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/8821429ef5fbd3d97503b707f14d2f3d.webm?t=1737972661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/8821429ef5fbd3d97503b707f14d2f3d.mp4?t=1737972661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build Your Dream Mall</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you want to replicate your favorite real-world shopping center or let your imagination run wild with a unique design, ultimately, the choice is yours! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from an array of shops and create a mall that stands out from the rest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/f188589ef474723b8bbae2e8038418f5.avif?t=1737972661\" width=616 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/e8389663a4bb92fb116dff739efaf82d.poster.avif?t=1737972661\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/e8389663a4bb92fb116dff739efaf82d.webm?t=1737972661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/e8389663a4bb92fb116dff739efaf82d.mp4?t=1737972661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize Every Detail</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who says all malls have to look the same? <br>With Mall Craze, you have the power to personalize every aspect of your mall. <br>Want a sleek, modern design? No problem. Prefer a cozy, rustic vibe?  <br>The options are there for you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/a6f298761d880eb2ece66b81f1041803.avif?t=1737972661\" width=616 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/bec543f4387909bf8e0c7021ced62d88.poster.avif?t=1737972661\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/bec543f4387909bf8e0c7021ced62d88.webm?t=1737972661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/bec543f4387909bf8e0c7021ced62d88.mp4?t=1737972661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Become the Manager</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once your mall is built, it's time to put on your managerial hat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hire experienced cashiers <i>(or make tough decisions and let underperforming employees go)</i>, launch strategic advertising campaigns, secure financing through bank loans, and fine-tune your pricing strategy to maximize profits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With smart decisions, your mall will financially thrive in no time! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/0394a00b5264260524ebbde239801018.avif?t=1737972661\" width=616 height=75 /></span><i>Curious to see how far your architectorial, creative & managerial talents can take you?</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/b2517ef4b328644f13b6d4e48f156e61.avif?t=1737972661\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever strolled through your local mall and thought to yourself: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“I could totally build something like this myself!”</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Well, now you can!</strong> Mall Craze is a Shopping Center Management game where you become the architect and owner of your very own mall! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/8821429ef5fbd3d97503b707f14d2f3d.poster.avif?t=1737972661\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/8821429ef5fbd3d97503b707f14d2f3d.webm?t=1737972661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/8821429ef5fbd3d97503b707f14d2f3d.mp4?t=1737972661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build Your Dream Mall</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you want to replicate your favorite real-world shopping center or let your imagination run wild with a unique design, ultimately, the choice is yours! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from an array of shops and create a mall that stands out from the rest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/f188589ef474723b8bbae2e8038418f5.avif?t=1737972661\" width=616 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/e8389663a4bb92fb116dff739efaf82d.poster.avif?t=1737972661\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/e8389663a4bb92fb116dff739efaf82d.webm?t=1737972661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/e8389663a4bb92fb116dff739efaf82d.mp4?t=1737972661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize Every Detail</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who says all malls have to look the same? <br>With Mall Craze, you have the power to personalize every aspect of your mall. <br>Want a sleek, modern design? No problem. Prefer a cozy, rustic vibe?  <br>The options are there for you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/a6f298761d880eb2ece66b81f1041803.avif?t=1737972661\" width=616 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/bec543f4387909bf8e0c7021ced62d88.poster.avif?t=1737972661\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/bec543f4387909bf8e0c7021ced62d88.webm?t=1737972661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/bec543f4387909bf8e0c7021ced62d88.mp4?t=1737972661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Become the Manager</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once your mall is built, it's time to put on your managerial hat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hire experienced cashiers <i>(or make tough decisions and let underperforming employees go)</i>, launch strategic advertising campaigns, secure financing through bank loans, and fine-tune your pricing strategy to maximize profits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With smart decisions, your mall will financially thrive in no time! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/0394a00b5264260524ebbde239801018.avif?t=1737972661\" width=616 height=75 /></span><i>Curious to see how far your architectorial, creative & managerial talents can take you?</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1223530/extras/b2517ef4b328644f13b6d4e48f156e61.avif?t=1737972661\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p>",
